<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5278619>
    dc:description "PLATE 69. A, B, D. Male genitalia. C. Head. E. Female, lateral view. A. Bocchus rubrithorax from India (from Olmi 2010). B. B. thai, holotype (from Olmi 2005a). C. B. viet, male paratype (from Olmi 1991). D. B. viet, male from Thailand. E. Thaumatodryinus sp. (from Olmi 1984). Length 6.5 mm. Scale bar 0.21 mm for A, 0.25 mm for B, 1.10 mm for C and 0.23 mm for D." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5278619/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5278632>
    dc:description "PLATE 73. Thaumatodryinus zhejiangensis, holotype. A. Dorsal view. Length 3.5 mm. B. Chela (from Xu et al. 2009b). Scale bar 0.38 mm for B." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5278632/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5278621>
    dc:description "PLATE 70. A. Tuft of long hairs on antennal segment. B–D. Chelae, holotypes. A. Thaumatodryinus sp., female (from Olmi 1984). B. Th. alienus (from Olmi 1987a). C. T. asiaticus (from Olmi 1984). D. T. beckeri (from Olmi 1991). Scale bar 0.21 mm for B, 0.18 mm for C and 0.44 mm for D." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5278621/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5278630>
    dc:description "PLATE 72. A. Dorsal view. B, C. Chelae, holotypes. A. Thaumatodryinus pasohensis, male from Brunei. Length 2.9 mm. B. Th. philippinus (from Olmi 1984). C. Th. sharkeyi (from Olmi 2011b). Scale bar 0.25 mm for B and C." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5278630/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5278626>
    dc:description "PLATE 71. A–C. Male genitalia. D–G. Chelae, holotypes. A. Thaumatodryinus hainanensis, holotype (from Xu et al. 2009b). B. Th. pasohensis from Brunei. C. Th. philippinus. D. T. malayanus (from Olmi 1984). E. Th. moganensis (from Xu et al. 2001b). F. Th. pasohensis (from Olmi 1991). G. Th. noyesi (from Olmi 1992). Scale bar 0.23 mm for A, B and G, 0.17 mm for C, 0.39 mm for D, 0.37 mm for E, 0.33 mm for F." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5278626/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

